50
00:03:25,260 --> 00:03:26,260
Don't you think it's strange?

51
00:03:34,200 --> 00:03:35,380
Why didn't I think of it?

52
00:03:35,770 --> 00:03:38,040
Could it be that she didn't die accidentally

53
00:03:38,700 --> 00:03:39,780
