100
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:55,800
So I can conclude

101
00:05:56,100 --> 00:05:57,540
this painting was also drawn by Shi Hu

102
00:05:58,330 --> 00:05:59,770
Besides, the paper used for this painting

103
00:06:00,010 --> 00:06:01,370
