246
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:25,000
Let's look around.

247
00:11:31,330 --> 00:11:32,990
[Xueyu Town]

248
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:40,800
We've searched for a long time,

249
00:11:41,180 --> 00:11:42,700
